name: I wanna be the Macho!
description:
A wacky adventure game about becoming macho!

Contains:

  • 5 difficult levels
  • Many devious traps
  • Absurd bosses
  • Retro video game and pop culture references

and more!

This game is intentionally supposed to be like early adventure fangames like "I wanna be the Tribute", "I wanna be the Ultimatum!", and "I wanna be the Fangame!"
